      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe carrier and a recent rod bearing service to ensure crankshaft longevity. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, and the braking system provides consistent bite with minimal fade. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the structural integrity and powertrain performance align with a well-sorted driver's car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
